high_descs: Turn around and go forwards towards the sink
Pick up the spatula to the right in the sink
Turn around and go back between the table and a counter to the right.  Turn right towards the counter
Open cabinet door and place the spatula on a plate in the cabinet
Pick up the plate with the spatula on it
Turn around and move towards the refrigerator and move between the refrigerator and the table before turning right towards the table
Place the plate with the spatula on it on top of the table to the right of the bowl and below the knife
anns.task_desc: Taking a plate with a spatula on it to a table

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the sink.
Pick up the spatula on the right.
Turn around and take three steps, then turn right and walk to the counter.
Open the cupboard on the bottom right.
Take the plate out of the bottom right cupboard.
Turn around and walk to the table, then turn right to face it.
Put the plate and spatula down on the table next to the brown bowl.
anns.task_desc: To get the spatula and plate.

high_descs: Turn to your left then cross the room head to the sink
Pick up the left turner in the sink
Turn to your left walk straight then turn right facing the right cabinet beside the oven
Open the cabinet on the right, put the turner on the plate
Pick up the plate with turner then close the cabinet
Turn to your right then head to the table
Put the plate with turner on the table beside the knife
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with turner on the table
